OL,3,CEx-police officer sentenced for child
OL,4,Csex offences and voyeurism offences
OL,6,FA former North Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Fofficer has been handed a suspended
OL,8,Fsentence for eight sex offences.
OL,10,FPaul Beckwith, 53, from York, pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty to three counts of possessing
OL,12,Findecent images of children and five
OL,13,Fcounts of voyeurism.
OL,15,FBeckwith was a serving Police
OL,16,FConstable with North Yorkshire Police
OL,17,Fwhen he was arrested on 17 November
OL,18,F2024 on suspicion of possessing
OL,19,Findecent images of children.
OL,21,FHe was suspended from duties.
