OL,3,CEx-police officer sentenced for child
OL,4,Csex offences and voyeurism offences
OL,6,FHe was dismissed from the force for
OL,7,Fgross misconduct when he was arrested
OL,8,Fagain in March 2025 for suspected
OL,9,Fvoyeurism and further indecent images
OL,10,Fof children offences.
OL,12,FThe former police constable was known
OL,13,Ffor supporting the father of Claudia
OL,14,FLawrence after her disappearance in
OL,15,F2009.
OL,17,FBeckwith was sentenced to 14 months'
OL,18,Fimprisonment, suspended for 18 months,
OL,19,Ffor three counts of possessing
OL,20,Findecent images of children and five
OL,21,Fcounts of voyeurism.
