OL,4,Csex offences and voyeurism offences
OL,6,FHe has also been made subject to a
OL,7,FCommunity Order and must undertake
OL,8,Frehabilitation activities and mental
OL,9,Fhealth treatment.
OL,11,FChief Constable Tim Forber said sexual
OL,12,Fimpropriety by police officers is a
OL,13,Fmatter of "significant national
OL,14,Fconcern."
OL,16,FHe added: "This misconduct is totally
OL,17,Fincompatible with being a police
OL,18,Fofficer, and the facts of this offence
OL,19,Fhave the potential to significantly
OL,20,Fundermine public confidence in
OL,21,Fpolicing."
